                {
                    "key": "message",
                    "value": "<size=30>LZ's Ear Wiggle Graph</size></size> \n\n<color=#ca6fde>by Lunazera</color>\nJuly 2026 (v2.1)\n\n▼——————————————— ▼\n\nThis is a little extra thing that works with the EarSway Pendulums. It will periodically wiggle a random ear :3 The pendulums will tilt your ears along with your head, raise ears with eyebrow raising, and lower them with your brows down. Also will wiggle if you blink.\n\nTo set up the EarSway Pendulum chains, just set the gameobject to your control bones for your ears.\n(if you have the tail graph, you could also change the \"EarWiggleTimer\" name to \"TailTimer\" to save on processing a bit)\n\n<b><size=20>Main Controls:</size></b>\n• Wiggle Min/Max Random Time = Sets the time range between each random ear wiggle\n• Wiggle Amount = How long your ear wiggles will last for (in ms)\n• Wiggle Speed = How fast the wiggle will move your pendulum. Set smaller to make slower movements\n\n<b><size=20><color=#008B8B>Blendshape Controls</b></size></color>\n• EarLeft - Moves left ear down\n• EarRight - Moves right ear down"
                }
            ],
            "posX": -846.994140625,
            "posY": 465.4835205078125,
            "path": "Nodes/MessageBoxNode",
